frontmatter.name: Vidit Kushwaha
frontmatter.bio: I'm Vidit Kushwaha, a final-year student doing my bachelor's of technology from the National Institute of Technology (NIT), Rourkela, and I'm a tech enthusiast, and I love creating applications that stay on the internet. I'm a self-taught developer and always looking for new ways to improve my skills and stay up-to-date with the latest technologies. I am passionate about creating clean and efficient code and love working on projects that challenge me.
